Title: Cloudflare 1.1.1.1  Incident on July 14, 2025
Description:

We‚Äôre deeply sorry for this outage.

This outage was the result of an internal configuration error and not the result of an attack or a BGP hijack. In this blog post, we‚Äôre going to talk about what the failure was, why it occurred, and what we‚Äôre doing to make sure this doesn‚Äôt happen again.
